# Type details

## FrequencyUnit

`FrequencyUnit` type is an alias for `Literal["days", "seconds", "microseconds", "milliseconds", "minutes", "hours", "weeks"]`.

## WindowType

`WindowType` type is an alias for `Literal["expanding", "rolling"]`.
